            }
          ],
          "type": "section"
        },
        {
          "name": "Vorvorak Bile (poison) Saving Throw DC 28 Fortitude; Maximum Duration 6 rounds; Stage 1 2d8 poison and sickened 1 (2 rounds); Stage 2 3d8 poison and sickened 2 (2 rounds); Stage 3 4d8 poison and sickened 3 (2 rounds)",
          "sources": [
